# Copy to .dev.vars for local development with `wrangler dev`.
#
# All values are OPTIONAL. Callers normally supply their own TripIt OAuth
# credentials per-request via the X-TripIt-* headers, so nothing is stored
# on the server.

# Optional fallback credentials for a private single-user deployment — all
# four must be set together. Leave unset for a shared server where every
# caller sends their own credentials. Mint access tokens once with
# `npm run authorize -- <consumer_key> <consumer_secret>`.
# TRIPIT_CONSUMER_KEY=your_consumer_key
# TRIPIT_CONSUMER_SECRET=your_consumer_secret
# TRIPIT_ACCESS_TOKEN=your_access_token
# TRIPIT_ACCESS_TOKEN_SECRET=your_access_token_secret

# Optional: enforce Cloudflare Access JWT validation in the Worker.
# Leave unset for local development.
# ACCESS_TEAM_DOMAIN=myteam
# ACCESS_APP_AUD=your_access_application_aud_tag
